        <item>
            <title>林超英：开冷气会通知大家　出梗图「唔好再问我有无开冷气」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/06/lamchiuying-report-safety-on-facebook/life-tech/green-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lamchiuying-report-safety-on-facebook</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/06/lamchiuying-report-safety-on-facebook/life-tech/green-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 08:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[健康]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[环保]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Luna Is A Bep]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[冷气]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[林超英]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1254881</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">前天文台台长林超英向来提倡环保，甚少开冷气的他长期在电费单上维持负七元。最近他就在自己的 Facebook 专页上向大家报平安表示自己没有热倒，感激广大市民在炎热天气下仍然关心他有没有开冷气。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254885 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/123135429-562x580.jpg" alt="林超英" width="562" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/123135429-562x580.jpg 562w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/123135429.jpg 872w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 562px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/lamchiuyinghk/posts/pfbid02e1pRuQjXkHs3ob1XNkNSNniqStje2YBzMmyRvuuFYifJciDYCzoxonigZpQWqXrVl?rdid=DHonRtnNabSLyD9w">Facebook @林超英 Lam Chiu Ying</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">天文台在昨日录得全年最高温记录的 35.4 度，林超英在 Facebook 上表示自己依旧没有开冷气。林超英在贴文中附上了自己的工作桌照片，桌上摆放了手提电脑和不同的文件，还摆放了一把小风扇。他表示自己都是在这样的工作环境，靠着一把小风扇渡过一天的工作。他强调自己实在太热也是会开冷气的，而且开冷气时会向大家交代，呼吁网民毋须天天询问他有否开冷气。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254886 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/12-2-508x580.jpg" alt="" width="508" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/12-2-508x580.jpg 508w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/12-2.jpg 789w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 508px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/lamchiuyinghk/posts/pfbid02e1pRuQjXkHs3ob1XNkNSNniqStje2YBzMmyRvuuFYifJciDYCzoxonigZpQWqXrVl?rdid=DHonRtnNabSLyD9w">Facebook @林超英 Lam Chiu Ying</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">林超英的贴文引来了不少的网民赞好，欣赏他为了环保而身体力行，更佩服他的坚持。林超英亦在留言区上分享了与说唱歌手 Luna Is A Bep 合作推出宣扬环保讯息的歌曲《超英歌》 MV 截图「唔好再问我有无开冷气」，重申如果有开冷气会通知大家。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/lamchiuyinghk/posts/pfbid02e1pRuQjXkHs3ob1XNkNSNniqStje2YBzMmyRvuuFYifJciDYCzoxonigZpQWqXrVl?rdid=DHonRtnNabSLyD9w">Facebook @林超英 Lam Chiu Ying</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NAf72Bwg3uA">Hong Kong 2050 is NOW</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/06/adac-test-reveals-the-effects-of-aircon-on-ev-range/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">德国最大汽车协会科学测试，空气调节对电动车续航力影响</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/06/lamchiuying-report-safety-on-facebook/life-tech/green-2/">林超英：开冷气会通知大家　出梗图「唔好再问我有无开冷气」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
