                <![CDATA[<p>美国跑步选手 Noah Lyles 在今届巴黎奥运以 9.784 秒佳绩取得男子 100 米比赛冠军，化身「男飞人」。Noah Lyles 比赛后在全球观众的目光下摆出「龟波气功」庆祝胜利，以经典动作致敬《龙珠》。此举引起大众热议，更被日本媒体称其为「世上跑得最快的动漫迷」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240805at-8.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254815" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240805at-8-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240805at-8-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot20240805at-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>现年 27 岁的 Noah Lyles 向来热爱日本文化，之前亦曾在 6 月的奥运选拔赛上，在起跑前向镜头炫耀《游戏王》的「蓝眼白龙」及「Exodia 禁忌之一」卡牌，并佩戴受《火影忍者》 启发的配饰。在总决赛后，日本体育报章《每日体育》更于头条上称 Noah Lyles 是「人类最快的御宅族」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/c726a3b6fceff61719d0.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254813" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/c726a3b6fceff61719d0-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/c726a3b6fceff61719d0-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/c726a3b6fceff61719d0.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>龙珠迷 Noah Lyles 在今年年初龙珠作者鸟山明逝世时，亦有于 X 上发文悼念致敬，称对失去传奇人物鸟山明感到非常悲伤，指鸟山明的作品永远影响他的生活。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">So sad to lose a legend Akira Toriyama<br />Ik his work has forever affected my life. <a href="https://t.co/KyDPRzr8ng">pic.twitter.com/KyDPRzr8ng</a></p><p>&mdash; Noah Lyles, OLY (@LylesNoah) <a href="https://twitter.com/LylesNoah/status/1766190938471211516?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 8, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.citizen.digital/sports/japan-hails-100m-champ-lyles-as-worlds-fastest-anime-fan-n347158">Citizen Digital</a>、<a href="https://nextshark.com/usa-runner-noah-lyles-yu-gi-oh-cards-olympic-trials">Next Shark</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/olympics/life-tech/sport-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">巴黎奥运「中国制」无处不在，阿里云提供直播技术 + 主导官方纪念品市场</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/cheungkalong-ig-spam-by-italian/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">张家朗 IG 被意大利人洗版闹偷金牌　意大利剑击联盟为赛果提抗议</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/summer-olympics-apple-maps-update/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Maps 推出更新，为巴黎奥运揭幕作准备</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/noah-lyles/game-channel/">奥运男飞人「龟波气功」庆祝，曾开跑前哂《游戏王》卡、被日媒称「最快的宅」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
